    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器游乐场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试试所有的武器：射击，把它们向敌人头上一扔，再把下一个拖过来，重复。用各种武器组合 — 从熟悉的手枪到真空炮（这是什么？）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/47dbec3e344f4eeaffac0f2987f65bb5.poster.avif?t=1766599243\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/47dbec3e344f4eeaffac0f2987f65bb5.webm?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/47dbec3e344f4eeaffac0f2987f65bb5.mp4?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>强大的魔法武装</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击、防御和支援魔法，应对各种情况。火球、电击、盾牌和召唤助手只是魔法的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/1b8785cb5b8b14626975d9a41cb6071a.poster.avif?t=1766599243\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/1b8785cb5b8b14626975d9a41cb6071a.webm?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/1b8785cb5b8b14626975d9a41cb6071a.mp4?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>疯狂的老板</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去揍坏蛋阴险的企业家魔法师、机械龙和其他传奇的机器魔法混蛋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/985c194033531733853f31d8fc90214c.poster.avif?t=1766599243\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/985c194033531733853f31d8fc90214c.webm?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/985c194033531733853f31d8fc90214c.mp4?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式动作游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破坏计算机，躲开子弹，注意警报按钮，同时用右手开枪，左手施放魔法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/e81f1f5d64945c964c30a7bc30bd3081.poster.avif?t=1766599243\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/e81f1f5d64945c964c30a7bc30bd3081.webm?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/e81f1f5d64945c964c30a7bc30bd3081.mp4?t=1766599243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>大量的敌对者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消灭无数的流氓、企业家、机器人、法师和其他恶棍！不要让他们以卑鄙的联合进攻和数量优势欺骗你。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>刺激的冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳进了机器魔法世界里的故事性射击场。你将遇到一个身体卡在机器人里的友好同事、贪图金钱的企业家魔法师和其他古怪的人。在这个已经非常疯狂的世界里，创造更多的混乱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无需连接到主机的游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在standalone模式中，享受无限制、无线的游戏体验。</p>",
